---
// Honest boundary panel — trust without sounding like a compliance page.
---
<section class="section" id="how-we-work">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="comp">
      <p class="eyebrow">How we work</p>
      <p class="statement" style="margin-top:.8rem">
        “Proxy” here means hands-on, real-time support — we prepare you thoroughly and support you
        round by round. We never impersonate candidates or fabricate experience.
      </p>
      <div class="comp-cols">
        <div class="do">
          <h4>What we do</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>JD-based interview preparation and real-time, round-wise support</li>
            <li>Real-time job support for daily tickets, debugging and deployments</li>
            <li>Profile engineering, marketing and managing to get more recruiter calls</li>
            <li>Honest positioning of your real skills and experience</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="dont">
          <h4>What we never do</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Attend interviews pretending to be you</li>
            <li>Do your job invisibly in your place</li>
            <li>Fabricate projects, employers or skills</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
